{"tid":1507414,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"售台戰機惹怒中国怎麼辦？ 美國防部長：繼續賣","createTime":"2019-08-26T06:46:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T09:17:12.000Z","uid":184679,"like":72,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"34fa9d2300d38c2c767d9e09b9a14eac88fbbae2","tid":1507414,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T06:46:00.000Z","msg":"美國務院日前批准對台軍售，66架F-16V戰機及其相關設備，成為1992年之後，美國再度宣布售台先進戰機，引發中國當局不滿。對此，美國防部長艾斯培(Mark Esper)日前接受電視台專訪時，被問到美對台軍售F-16V戰機，已激怒中國，未來美方會怎麼做時，他表示，之後還會繼續賣下去。<br />\n<br />\n艾斯培指出，美國並非首次向台灣出售武器，當然也不是第一次出售F-16戰機，所以他推測，美國對台灣的軍售會持續下去。至於被問到美中貿易戰問題，雙方關係處於敏感時刻之際，且貿易談判還在進行中，對此，他則回應，中國似乎總是處於敏感時刻中。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://globalnewstv.com.tw/201908/78923/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fglobalnewstv.com.tw%2F201908%2F78923%2F&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY%2FGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=26ac658c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://globalnewstv.com.tw/201908/78923/</a>"},{"pid":"b1be124519b45662a33da2920dc1b831312c6ff2","tid":1507414,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T06:46:42.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個post宣傳一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GJMrJb.jpg&h=cb7c9807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n901 和你塞  13:00 見   <a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY%2FGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=c9b74cca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"2486c0c8739a1643f7c07346891dcd8f92426d85","tid":1507414,"uid":56052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T06:46:59.000Z","msg":"(外國文宣) 大家係咪miss 左一粒核彈？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1507386\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1507386</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"29f4f92026c2ca7a8dc3f40c7c932296bbb855e1","tid":1507414,"uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2